descriptionHtml:
Self Study made easy with this app.
This is a good learning app for IIT JEE Main,IIT JEE Advance, BITSAT, VITEEE, WBJEE, MHTCET, KCET, UPSEE, COMEDK, EAMCET ,PJET ,OJEE and it cater to the learning needs of students in classes 11th ,12th and beyond.
This app provides you with Physics , Chemistry And Mathematics study material with Solutions.
Get solution of every question without worrying where to get solution.
Material consists of theory too so brush up essentials before moving forward.
App contains every chapter.You don't need to buy costly books or other study material.
So go ahead get this app.
Start preparing.
There are famous coachings such as Vibrant Academy, Allen Coaching Institute , Resonance Institute, Nucleus Education and they provide good study material too but lack in providing complete solutions of problems or solutions provided in classes vary from teacher to teacher.
IIT JEE Mains and IIT JEE Advance preparation is a very long process but worth it.
Rather being a fan of reading theories and studying notes of different faculties students should give practicing questions and solving material thier prime priority.

The Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) is a group of educational institutes in India set up by the government to produce high quality scientists, engineers and technologists.

Designated as institutes of national importance, the IITs were set up to boost industrial development and manufacturing by creating an elite pool of engineering talent within the country.

Governed by the IIT Act of 1961, the IITs are autonomous institutes with their own boards of directors.
